Missing values imputation from a MSnSet object

Source: R/missingValuesImputation_ProteinLevel.R
impute_fixed_value.Rd

This method is a wrapper to objects of class MSnSet and imputes missing values with a fixed value.

impute_fixed_value(x, value)

Arguments

x

An assay of a SummarizedExperiment
value

A float .

Value

The object obj which has been imputed

Author

Samuel Wieczorek

Examples

utils::data(Exp1_R25_pept, package='DAPARdata')
impute_fixed_value(assay(Exp1_R25_pept[seq_len(1000)], 2), 0.001)
